      "review_summary": "The PR adds opt-in `${VAR:json}` parsing for whole-value config env references, write-back preservation for structured values, and focused config tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +110, Tests +122. Total +232 across 4 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. by source inspection: current main resolves string config values through `substituteString`, which returns strings, so an env var cannot materialize an array/object before schema validation. I did not execute code because this review is read-only.",
